headline: MWC 2025: TGT Technology Global Unveils Global 5G Cloud Communications + Satellite IoT Solution, Empowering Japanese Enterprises with Ubiquitous Connectivity
summary: At the MWC 2025, TGT Technology Global, a world-leading cloud communications platform provider, officially launched its "Global 5G Cloud Communications + Satellite IoT Solution." This pioneering solution achieves seamless, ubiquitous coverage across land, sea, air, and remote areas for the first time through the deep integration of 5G and multi-orbit satellite IoT technologies. headline: A Caller Told Dave Ramsey His Girlfriend Was Overspending On His Credit Card. Ramsey's Response? 'You Gave Your Roommate A Credit Card!'
summary: A 23-year-old caller on a recent episode of “The Ramsey Show” had a tough question: How do you get on the same page financially with your girlfriend? She has a steady job and brings in her own income, but he was covering rent, groceries and other essentials. On top of that, he had given her a card linked to his account for expenses.
